{"tid":698160,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果終於跟上潮流了！iOS 12新增中國二維碼掃描","createTime":"2018-06-11T12:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T04:59:18.000Z","uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"7aad42c1aa11c6435edc24d2bc5774fa5d37182e","tid":698160,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:31:16.000Z","msg":"隨著國產大軍的不斷發展，現在蘋果這個巨頭在中國市場的地位也開始搖搖欲墜了，現在不再是蘋果獨霸的市場，所以估計很多消費者也開始看到蘋果在一些產品逐漸的妥協的行動了。而在6月5日最新發佈的iOS 12 系統中，其在控制中心也突破性地新增了一個二維碼的掃描功能，另一反面也反映出評估終於意識到在<strong>中國二維碼</strong>的重要性了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/202901_8d5dfb0f7721a1872961f99877f2f252.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F202901_8d5dfb0f7721a1872961f99877f2f252.png&h=c8b1a24d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過作為線上支付的大國，這次蘋果在iOS 12 新增的二維碼工作儘管在一定程度上給用戶們帶來方便，但是其實相對更多用戶而言，大家會更加傾向於微信和支付寶支付。畢竟用蘋果手機相機掃描的體驗，在目前而言並不是十分好用，識別度相對微信和支付寶等線上支付而言還是比較低的。<br />\n<br />\n在使用體驗上，筆者就給大家舉一個例子，就是我們在進行線上支付的時候，無論是微信還是支付寶即使在很遠的地方也能十分精確地識別到二維碼，其還能夠自動拉近或者拉遠進行識別，但是蘋果的二維碼識別卻顯得不是那麼「智能」了，目前僅僅對近距離的二維碼能夠識別，稍微遠點的都會造成識別失敗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/202837_c743ec0c3e4b4ba804c56019350bc4e6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F202837_c743ec0c3e4b4ba804c56019350bc4e6.png&h=2ec522aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沒有對比就沒有傷害，畢竟二維碼在中國市場來說已經是十分普遍的事情了，看來蘋果想要僅僅栓住國內的消費者，看來還需要多下點功夫了。<br />\n<br />\n<code>利申：轉貼咋我</code><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad34596fd5d61a29894679dec182a5fcb4872f3","tid":698160,"uid":1130,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:33:00.000Z","msg":"但係明明本身相機app都讀到QR code 又要整多粒制做乜鳩 <br />\n<br />\n驚D蝗太蠢唔知？"},{"pid":"8274053507205ce8c4c66b0185631fc27086097f","tid":698160,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:33:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係明明本身相機app都讀到<span style=\"color: red;\">China</span> QR code 又要整多粒制做乜鳩 <br />\n<br />\n驚D蝗太蠢唔知？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d981a9438b94898b79da340c44470430e6b11f1c","tid":698160,"uid":36822,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:35:13.000Z","msg":"若然屬實,中國便會是贏家"},{"pid":"261c36a7acc0a5515e539379cb39863b62f5ba6b","tid":698160,"uid":37820,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:38:59.000Z","msg":"有Apple pay唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為啲中國人申請唔到信用卡？"},{"pid":"31c3c0f05fb32fea597b77b09cfd8ee6307d7015","tid":698160,"uid":4525,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:41:26.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"86568add924a29d81ed7c1a25eeb77a42a23cd15","tid":698160,"uid":164092,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"261c36a7acc0a5515e539379cb39863b62f5ba6b","tid":698160,"uid":37820,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:38:59.000Z","msg":"有Apple pay唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為啲中國人申請唔到信用卡？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:46:06.000Z","msg":"因為中國人冇信用？"},{"pid":"ec357357cf0d869ff2a520462d5affeabb90bc49","tid":698160,"uid":183991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825daebfb1be9e3697afe2d2c8bd08373e850067","tid":698160,"uid":12628,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"86568add924a29d81ed7c1a25eeb77a42a23cd15","tid":698160,"uid":164092,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"261c36a7acc0a5515e539379cb39863b62f5ba6b","tid":698160,"uid":37820,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-