s/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為啲中國人申請唔到信用卡？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:46:06.000Z","msg":"因為中國人冇信用？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:55:22.000Z","msg":"你做銀行，係會唔會發信用卡比共國人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:01:08.000Z","msg":"另一方面<br />\n贏國無鋪頭識用信用卡"},{"pid":"840089b138771c977c29d47ed6c78225d636557e","tid":698160,"uid":183991,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:04:19.000Z","msg":"呢啲po又會轉左去屌支那 跟住內文就當睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491bf8f2d2aafbb67f9a317271f7e660ed9d2c7f","tid":698160,"uid":51174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:11:51.000Z","msg":"Scan qr code講到新野咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc55997da59e752c4caebedd5b55f4843625a4d7","tid":698160,"uid":50018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:37:33.000Z","msg":"首先呢，QR Code 係由日本Denso Wave 於1994年發明嘅資料傳輸規格，我唔知點解支那人會覺得某兩隻pay 有qr code 而好似如獲至寶咁認晒叻打晒飛機囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「QRコード」を開発。本学OBの原昌宏氏が欧州発明家賞で「Popular Prize」を受賞しました<br />\n<br />\n株式会社デンソーウェーブの原昌宏氏がQRコード開発で欧州発明家賞（European Inventor Award）授賞式において、Popular Prizeを受賞しました。<br />\nPopular Prizeは欧州特許庁ウェブサイトやFacebookから一般投票によって選ばれる賞で、受賞は日本人初の快挙となります。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">原氏</span>は法政大学第二高等学校から、1980年法政大学工学部電気工学科（現在の理工学部電気電子工学科）を卒業され、<span style=\"color: red;\">日本電装（現デンソー）に入社。技術開発チームを率いて、1994年に「QRコード」を開発・発表されました。QRコードは今や世界中で使われる国際規格です。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hosei.ac.jp/NEWS/kyoiku_kenkyu/140619.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hosei.ac.jp%2FNEWS%2Fkyoiku_kenkyu%2F140619.html&d=K1Yw%2BttpgbXCZhAh9ATRg7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=5e590a55\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hosei.ac.jp/NEWS/kyoiku_kenkyu/140619.html</a>"},{"pid":"8dfde4fffcb42837b2d4c7f643d0e4a3f9a98dd9","tid":698160,"uid":1130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8274053507205ce8c4c66b0185631fc27086097f","tid":698160,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:33:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係明明本身相機app都讀到<span style=\"color: red;\">China</span> QR code 又要整多粒制做乜鳩 <br />\n<br />\n驚D蝗太蠢唔知？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:39:05.000Z","msg":"你升12睇下啦  㩒落去都係開相機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9a67114ea6fc79138018b6fde3233d01c39ec8","tid":698160,"uid":1049,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d981a9438b94898b79da340c44470430e6b11f1c","tid":698160,"uid":36822,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:35:13.000Z","msg":"若然屬實,中國便會是贏家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:51:42.000Z","msg":"若然係假，蘋果爭競爭力將會下降，國產手機將會擴大市場佔有率，中國或許會成為最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50998414e7223868fe2e1b62c5c6237a3e323dc0","tid":698160,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"840089b138771c977c29d47ed6c78225d636557e","tid":698160,"uid":183991,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:04:19.000Z","msg":"呢啲po又會轉左去屌支那 跟住內文就當睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:54:19.000Z","msg":"開卷有益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過你講下內文有咩好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢篇文大陸網睇到,我譯左繁體先post<br />\n本身篇文都無乜留言lol"},{"pid":"54bc7dcf9f3cfea242429e4ec3cc3b2ca57ea32c","tid":698160,"uid":183991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:22:50.000Z","msg":"叫班死忠入黎支持下apple出既新功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br /